item.title: about
item.description: I’m a software developer from Toronto. I’m interested in machine learning algorithms for document reading and comprehension. I’m currently fun-employed working on personal projects: machine reading models in TensorFlow, an arcade-style game in OpenGL/C++, and a frontend for Keras in React.
